Text.string: Whatchu want?!
This here's a black market, so buy somethin' and git!
Buy somethin'! Or get lost.
I don't got all day, skag licker.
Just buy somethin' already.
If you up in my grill, you better buy somethin'!
Pick somethin'! I got all day, but not for you!
You can knock on a door—you want a damn prize or somethin'?
I was expectin' you—to get LOST!
“My favorite customer!” said NO ONE! EVER!
What the hell's a Loot-O-Gram? Let's see what's in it... it's crap!
A Loot-O-Gram? You find this in a cave or somethin'? Bring crap, get crap! That's what Mama used to say.
Loot-O-Grams? Why you bringing me this crap? I ain't no Craptarch!
I'll take your Loot-O-Grams! Let's see, what's the exchange rate... it's crap!
You brought this all the way back to the ship? Well, here's what you been waitin' for!
Stole that.
Found that.
Don't know where that came from.
Blood cleaned off REAL nice.
That's a deal.
Buy it and get lost!
You look, you buy!
Just buy somethin', ya turd blossom.
C'mon! I ain't got all day!
Gimme your Eridium first.
Yup.
All right.
What else you buyin'?
Pay and get out!
No takebacks.
Now we're talkin'!
Uh huh.
That's a good'un.
Don't tell no one where you got that.
This never happened, understand?
Come back never!
Scram!
I'll be waitin'! And watchin'.
Thanks for the Eridium, ya turd farmer!
Next time, bring some damn flowers.
Goodbye! Just another word for “get the hell outta here”!
Finally, heh! Now I can work on my damn novel.
Next time, there'll be TRAPS!
Good riddance, heh!
Stay out!
Don't be wastin' my time just lookin'!
Don't just stand there! Buy somethin'!
I don't sell nothin' to amateurs. This here's VETERAN gear, kid!
You lost, or just nosy?
Well, you're here now, so might as well spend some Eridium.
I only sell to vet—uh, veterinarians, heh! Whatever.
Already forgot about ya.
Finally, heh! Thought you'd NEVER leave!
Don't come round again unless you're spendin'!
Get gone and stay that way!
Hey, uh, thanks for stoppin' by... is what an IDIOT would say! Get spaced, jerkwad!
Heh, thought I'd NEVER get rid of that crap!
Enjoy! Sucker.
Don't tell nobody I gave you that! They'll all want one.
Don't ask me where I got it. Just take it and git!
I don't wanna see that crap ever again!
This here's for buyin', not for eyein'!
Serious buyers only, buster!
That there's for VAULT HUNTERS, not jokers like you!
I'm throwin' this junk out if you don't buy it quick!
This crap is special. You want it or not?
